{"tid":203081,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有個群腳仔男朋友","createTime":"2017-04-16T04:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T15:47:36.000Z","uid":22136,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f5dabc78423dfc4025b28feb250ebb2735113c8","tid":203081,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:35:38.000Z","msg":"一直我都以為係比較孝順佢媽咪<br />\n但最近好似發現越來越唔妥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n琴晚佢同我講如果第時個老婆唔同佢媽咪一齊住就要&ldquo;dum&quot;左個老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我覺得同未來奶奶住唔係一個問題 而係佢琴日話如果佢媽咪再老啲就唔會同佢講道理<br />\n而係要遷就哂佢 <br />\n我就話 咁如果佢真係無理取鬧咁恰我呢？<br />\n佢個回覆都係一樣<br />\n同埋我諗返走佢同我講過佢岀街會拖媽咪隻手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又有時會同我講其實佢好中意佢媽咪 <br />\n但唔識表達<br />\n我即刻好驚 雖然唔係話一定會同佢結婚<br />\n但始終拍拖最終嘅目的都係想結婚 <br />\n我已經分唔清佢係孝順定咩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我本身家庭關係唔太好 唔係好感受過家庭溫暖<br />\n所以想問下係咪我諗太多 只係我男朋友比較孝順<br />\n定係真係有小小戀母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3887b66e135f60ceb3be9b26383942ffff68363","tid":203081,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c230b5316968e8ad2b22853d5b039add0dced9cd","tid":203081,"uid":106130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:41:26.000Z","msg":"孝順姐，中意自己老豆老母好正常姐<br />\n好過果啲當老豆老母係狗既人<br />\n我覺得一個人孝順識飲水思源既人唔衰得去邊"},{"pid":"93eac35d03e3aa276bdbf0e14646d403a30858b4","tid":203081,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:42:34.000Z","msg":"咁叫孝順<br />\n死港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma